                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5622" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0852</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8976 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">转型期筹资的困境：谁更适合当股东？——基于山西吉利尔潞绸集团的案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The dilemma of financing in transitional period: Who are better suited to be shareholders?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王东升，田亚楠，任春敏，贾婳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西吉利尔潞绸集团织造股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">转型；股东异质性；风险匹配；团队技能组成；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> transformation; Heterogeneity of shareholders; Risk matching; Team skill composition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为承载“传承丝绸文明，重塑潞绸辉煌”历史使命的现代企业，山西吉利尔潞绸集团是周恩来总理亲点的、承载国家“东桑西移”第二个五年计划的重点项目。2008年企业改制，由国企转变为民营企业，在董事长王淑琴的带领下逐渐成为山西知名中高端礼品企业。2013年面临礼品市场的快速崩塌，管理层决定通过转型谋发展，采用聚焦战略以实现占领高端丝绸婚被市场。本案例以转型期股东应如何选择为主题，回顾了自2013年以来坎坷的转型历程，面对完全陌生的市场和“零”客户基础，在资金、技术、市场、人才存在约束的情况下，企业既需要筹措资本以支撑扩张的需要，也需要通过融资引入志同道合的合作伙伴以赋能吉利尔转型发展。
本案例重点讨论三个关键问题：（1）转型期筹资方式的选择；（2）股东选择中投资者价值观相同与足额资本提供的取舍；（3）“资合”（出资者财务资源能否满足要求）与“人合”（出资者拥有的非财务资源与企业发展的契合度）的权衡等关键问题。对股东背后的资源和能力进行评估分析，以构建一个优势互补、技能突出的管理团队。旨在引导学员加深对转型期企业股东选择的理解与认识，同时对“资本+”时代如何选择股东提出自己的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a modern enterprise carrying the historical mission of &quot;inheriting silk civilization and reshaping silk brilliance&quot;, Shanxi Jillier Silk Group is the key project of the second five-year plan of Zhou Enlai&#39;s prime minister&#39;s pro-point and carrying the country&#39;s &quot;East-Sanxi Shift&quot;. In 2008, the enterprise restructuring, from state-owned enterprises to private enterprises, under the leadership of Chairman Wang Shuqin gradually become Shanxi well-known high-end gift enterprises. Faced with the rapid collapse of the gift market in 2013, management decided to develop through a transformation and adopt a focus strategy to capture the high-end silk wedding market. This case takes the theme of how shareholders in transition should choose, reviews the difficult transformation process since 2013, in the face of completely unfamiliar market and &quot;zero&quot; customer base, in the case of capital, technology, market, talent constraints, enterprises need to raise capital to support the need for expansion, but also through financing to introduce like-minded partners to enable Jilier transformation and development.
This case focuses on three key issues: (1) the choice of financing methods for the transition period;(2) the trade-offs between the same investor values and the full amount of capital offered in the shareholder&#39;s choice, and (3) the trade-off between &quot;capital&quot; (whether the financial resources of the funder can meet the requirements) and &quot;people&quot;, the fit of non-financial resources owned by the funder and the development of the enterprise. Assess and analyze the resources and capabilities behind shareholders to build a management team with complementary strengths and skills. The aim is to guide the students to deepen their understanding and understanding of the shareholders&#39; choice in the transition period, and at the same time put forward their own thoughts on how to choose the shareholders in the &quot;capital plus&quot; era.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《战略管理》、《高级财务管理理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业经营模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
